title: Dakine Leanne Pelosi Womens Team Heli Pro 18L Pack
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2015 Leanne Pelosi Womens Team Heli Pro 18L Pack.
Features: 
- Contoured harness designed specifically to fit a woman's frame
- Vertical snowboard carry
- Diagonal ski carry
- Fleece lined goggle pocket
- Hydration compatible
- Laptop sleeve
- Fits most 14" laptops
- Organizer pocket
- Padded waist belt
- Integrated rescue whistle / sternum strap
